A fixed-price [exchange](currency) where bitcoins can be bought and sold.  

Language: Korean only.

A Korean-language introduction to Bitcoin can be found at [www.buybitcoin.co.kr](http://www.buybitcoin.co.kr) and a Korean translation of [[Multibit]] is available (1.1).

##Buy

* Buy bitcoins with South Korean won.

##Sell

* Trade your bitcoins for South Korean won.

##History

The launched was announced on September 27, 2012 (4.1).

